  <constraints>
    <constraint source="project">**Phase exit gate requires user sign-off per CLAUDE.md Confirmation Triggers.** Compose the report, then PAUSE for user go/no-go to Phase C.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">This is a documentation gate — no scenario re-execution; cite evidence references only.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">BFF publish-size — confirm cumulative R6 delta across Phase B is within ≤+5 MB R6 total budget per NFR-02. Report cumulative delta in exit-gate report.</constraint>
